Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Investment Management
AdvisorShares Trust operates as an investment management company. The Company offers portfolio management, equities, fixed income, commodities, funds, investment strategies, financial planning, and advisory services. AdvisorShares Trust serves customers in the States of Maryland and Texas.




