 Mr.               Robert H                Morgan
Morgan Law Offices, a P.C.

                Morgan Law Offices, a PC is operated by Robert H. Morgan.  Mr. Morgan received his bachelor's degree in 1972 from the University of Oregon and received his MBA from Santa Clara University in 1975.  Mr. Morgan graduated Summa Cum Laude from Santa Clara University in 1978 and was admitted to the California State Bar that year.  Mr. Morgan has had an active law practice in San Jose since 1978
              
