^ Stern, Richard. "Fund.com Subsidiary, AdvisorShares, Partners with BNY Mellon and WCM Investment Management to Launch WCM/BNY Mellon Focused Growth ADR ETF". PR Newswire. 
^ "AdvisorShares Launches Four Gold ETFs". Financial Advisor Magazine. 
^ "AdvisorShares". Nasdaq. 
